Uttarakhand Covid-19 Daily Report: 14 June (9 PM)

34 new positive cases of Covid-19 and 34 recoveries reported in #Uttarakhand  today. Total cases in the hill-State stands at 1819 including 1111 recoveries and 24 fatalities. 

#COVID19India  #Covid_19 #Covid_19india https://t.co/agfQudaO1a
